snippet.title: Spell Crisis - Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X and Steam
snippet.description:
With pixel art and 1990s-style music, Spell Crisis is a 2D action platformer with exploration elements. Coming soon to consoles and PC.
